OL,3,CWhat counts as cyberflashing and what
OL,4,Cis the punishment?
OL,6,FCyberflashing became a criminal
OL,7,Foffence on January 31 along with a
OL,8,Fnumber of other measures put in place
OL,9,Fto protect people online.
OL,11,FIt follows campaigning from who became
OL,12,Fa victim of image-based abuse last
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FWhat is cyberflashing?
OL,17,FCyberflashing is the act of sending
OL,18,Funsolicited explicit images, usually
OL,19,Fon social media or dating apps.
